This software package is for testing EE1 on harmonization between NSST and PDPC. 
The corresponding proposal found in JVETC0042.

Modification: NSST index is coded/sent regardless of PDPC index

The following macro settings are used for testing.

EE1- Test4 macro setting (NSST and PDPC are appropriately decoupled w/o 2nd transform kernel modification)

#define JVET_C0042_NSST_PDPC                              1
#define JVET_C0053_C0063_NSST_IMPROVEMENTS                0 
#define JVET_C0053_C0063_USE_8x8_NSST                     0        
#define JVET_C0053_C0063_NSST_LM                          0

EE1- Test5 macro setting (NSST and PDPC are appropriately decoupled with new transform kernels)

#define JVET_C0042_NSST_PDPC                              1
#define JVET_C0053_C0063_NSST_IMPROVEMENTS                1 
#define JVET_C0053_C0063_USE_8x8_NSST                     1        
#define JVET_C0053_C0063_NSST_LM                          0